00:03:46.720 --> 00:03:47.220
AI-san,

00:03:47.840 --> 00:03:50.000
What should I do?"

00:03:50.520 --> 00:03:51.660
I see!

00:03:51.980 --> 00:03:52.480
This!

00:03:52.880 --> 00:03:53.500
You know

00:03:53.800 --> 00:03:54.940
If you like that person,

00:03:55.280 --> 00:03:56.660
you should cater to their preferences

00:03:56.660 --> 00:03:58.540
Fireworks displays and summer festivals can be,

00:03:58.540 --> 00:03:59.500
gone separate,

00:03:59.500 --> 00:04:00.780
friends or something,

00:04:00.880 --> 00:04:02.520
make some and go with them

00:04:02.920 --> 00:04:04.520
and go somewhere she likes

00:04:04.700 --> 00:04:06.740
If she doesn’t like rowdy places

00:04:06.740 --> 00:04:08.000
go to a quiet place

00:04:08.000 --> 00:04:09.040
like the sea or something?

00:04:09.100 --> 00:04:09.600
How’s that?

00:04:09.640 --> 00:04:11.640
And take it easy at that quiet place

00:04:12.240 --> 00:04:13.800
if that is possible

00:04:14.980 --> 00:04:15.640
research

00:04:15.800 --> 00:04:17.800
places that she likes

00:04:18.100 --> 00:04:19.380
and go together

00:04:19.380 --> 00:04:20.760
to that place she likes

00:04:21.180 --> 00:04:22.900
