00:04:24.480 --> 00:04:26.480
you could also go the watch the fireworks together

00:04:26.480 --> 00:04:27.700
looking at the fireworks hand in hand

00:04:27.700 --> 00:04:29.420
in a quiet park

00:04:30.220 --> 00:04:30.920
sounds good right?

00:04:30.920 --> 00:04:32.400
At the summer festival,

00:04:32.400 --> 00:04:33.620
there are a lot of small

00:04:33.620 --> 00:04:37.460
places that get a lot bigger, so make sure to do research.

00:04:38.840 --> 00:04:40.140
