00:04:40.560 --> 00:04:42.280
means you guys haven't started dating yet, so

00:04:42.280 --> 00:04:43.540
good luck! Next one!

00:04:45.560 --> 00:04:47.740
Ah, Morito! tell me, what's on your mind

00:04:48.600 --> 00:04:50.120
just say it

